predict.SL.halglmnet

Source: R/halglmnet.R
predict.SL.halglmnet.Rd

Predict method for objects of class SL.halglmnet

# S3 method for SL.halglmnet
predict(
  object,
  newdata,
  remove_extra_cols = FALSE,
  add_missing_cols = FALSE,
  ...
)

Arguments

object

A fitted object of class glmnet.
newdata

A matrix of new observations on which to obtain predictions.
remove_extra_cols

A logical indicating whether extra columns should be removed.
add_missing_cols

A logical indicating whether missing columns should be added to make the newdata and training data consistent.
...

Placeholder (ignored).

Value

A numeric vector of predictions from a SL.halglmnet object based on the provided newdata.
